reviewText: its like the movie teeth but with no blood and lots of nudity

This movie  doesnt pretend like most Hollywood junk. At the same time it doesnt have much of message either. The director is clearly professional and it works against movie. But why I gave it excellent? Because it is.
It connected to men's reality  and imagination. Yes, it gives me  my world. What is missing? Political message as life always connected to politics. Similar man's movie will be--The glamorous life of ....
